---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from '../../lib/site';
---

<Layout
  title="About the Project"
  description="Why Sight Scout exists: a friendly, honest tool that helps parents stay engaged with their child's vision and leads families toward eye care professionals, never away from them."
>
  <h1>About the project.</h1>

  <section class="mt-10">
    <p class="max-w-prose text-lg text-ink/90">
      Sight Scout is a small, independent project. It started in March 2024 with a simple
      frustration: amblyopia is the most common cause of preventable vision loss in children,
      it responds well to early treatment, and it still gets missed all the time because kids
      don't complain and screening between checkups is patchy.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-prose text-lg text-ink/90">
      We believe parents deserve friendly, honest tools that make it easier to stay engaged
      with their child's vision. And we believe the job of such a tool is to lead families
      toward eye care professionals, never to stand in for them. Everything about Sight
      Scout, from the copy on this site to the math in the activity, follows from those two
      beliefs.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10">
    <h2 class="text-lg">Contact</h2>
    <p class="mt-3">
      <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`} class="font-semibold text-teal hover:text-teal-dark">{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>
    </p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink/60">We read everything.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
